   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_RTC01_1825_08_25_page01.jpg"/>
            <p>
               <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss Edgeworth</persName>s Compliments<lb/>
               to the Editor of <title ref="./Workography.xml#Frien1">
                  <hi rend="underline">Friendship's</hi>
                  <lb/>
                  <hi rend="underline"> Offering"</hi>
               </title> - She has received<lb/>
               safely the pages of her M<hi rend="superscript">s</hi>
               <lb/>
               and thanks him for his <choice>
                  <orig>punc<lb/>
               tuality</orig>
                  <reg>punctuality</reg>
               </choice> - <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Miss E.</persName> now sends<lb/>
               to <persName ref="./Personography.xml#RelfL1">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Relfe</persName> an extract from<lb/>
               a letter from an American<lb/>
               friend of hers - If it should<lb/>
               suit M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>. <persName ref="./Personography.xml#HervT1">Hervey</persName>s views it<lb/>
               as in his service for insertion<lb/>
               in the <title ref="./Workography.xml#Ladys1">Lady's Remembrancer</title>
               <lb/>
               or <title ref="./Workography.xml#Frien1">Friendships Offering</title> - If<lb/>
               it should not suit him he<lb/>
               will have the goodness to<lb/>
               return it under cover to<lb/>
            </p>
            <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_Princeton_RTC01_1825_08_25_page02.jpg"/>
            <p>the <persName ref="./Personography.xml#ParsL1">Earl of Rosse</persName>
               <lb/>
               <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Parsonstown-House_IE">Parson's Town Ireland</placeName>.<lb/>
            </p>
            <closer>
               <dateline> when="1825-08-25"&gt;Aug<hi rend="superscript">t</hi>. 25<hi rend="superscript">h</hi> 1825
                     <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE">Edgeworth's Town</placeName>
               </dateline>
            </closer>
